      "description": "<div><p>Imagine a world where time stops until you start moving! Everything around you suddenly pauses if you stand still. These brilliant game mechanics were first introduced by the famous game SuperHot and have been loved by millions of gamers since. GoGoMan combined their unique, funky art style with the game mechanics inspired by SuperHot to create <strong>Time Shooter</strong>! When fans of Time Shooter requested a sequel with more maps, levels, and new types of weapons, GoGoMan responded with <strong>Time Shooter 2</strong> in March 2022, offering an enhanced game where you can smash enemies to pieces and dodge attacks.</p><p>With its clever concept and unusual art style, <strong>Time Shooter 2</strong> definitely stands apart from other Shoot 'Em All games. Control the flow of time as you strategize your every move. Use your pistol to smash enemies to pieces, fire with a rifle, and take down multiple foes with a gas cylinder explosion. Grab weapons from enemies and throw objects at your opponents. Everything moves in slow motion if you're playing slowly!</p><h2>Controls</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Move Mouse:</strong> Aim</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>WASD: </strong>Movement</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>LMB:</strong> Pick up / Shoot</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>RMB: </strong>Throw</li></ul><h2>How to Play Time Shooter 2</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\">Start from level 1 by pressing start. You'll spawn behind a table with different types of weapons on it.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Pick your weapon with the left mouse button.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Use WASD to move around. You'll see that foes will come closer as you move.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">For long-range enemies, use rifles and shotguns. Aim with the mouse and shoot by left-clicking.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Use the right mouse button to throw objects (such as rocks, axes, etc.) at enemies. Be careful not to throw any guns with ammo, as they will break and waste all the ammunition.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Remember, you can hold only one weapon at a time. When you run out of ammo or throw a weapon, pick up the nearest one to keep going.</li></ul><div><h2>Tips and Tricks</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\">One of the best features of Time Shooter 2 is that you have lots of reaction time when enemies attack if you move slowly.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">As you progress through the levels, enemies will become better armed and increase in number. So, it's wise to use your weapons based on the enemies' positions. Avoid wasting bullets on close-range enemies and save them for long-range encounters.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">To clear multiple enemies at once, throw a gas cylinder to create an explosion.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Collect weapons from defeated foes if you need them.</li></ul></div><h2>Developer</h2><p>Time Shooter 2 was developed by <strong>GoGoMan</strong>, known for creating funny shooter games with quirky characters and unique gameplay mechanics. If you enjoy GoGoMan's style, you can also try <a>You vs 100 Skibidi Toilets</a>, where you face off against a horde of strange toilets in a fast-paced and funny shooter game online.</p><h2>More Games Like This</h2><p>If you enjoy Time Shooter 2, you'll also like <a>Funny Shooter Bro</a>, which brings a humorous twist to the shooter genre with bizarre maps and sound effects. This lighthearted game contrasts relaxing animations with chaotic gameplay for online gamers!</p><figure></figure></div>",
