      "play_url": "https://voxiom.io/",
      "description": "<div><p>You are welcome here if you are looking for a game like Minecraft or Fortnite! <strong>Voxiom io</strong> is a multiplayer sandbox game where you craft and build stuff and engage in pixel battles. There are four modes, each with different aspects of the open world. You may be running from toxic fog or caught by an enemy with a gun in one of the most challenging fps io games.</p><h2>Voxiom io Overview</h2><p>As in every sandbox game, you can create your gaming experiences by your choices in this lol shooting. But apart from other sandbox games, Voxiom io offers open-world and battle-royale options for its players. You will be playing with other online players worldwide. They can be an excellent support for you or a real threat.</p><p>You must prepare yourself for every attack because everyone can do anything here to survive. You will have a Shovel, a Combat Assault Rifle and a Strike Pistol in the beginning. Craft more advanced guns through the workbenches for more power!</p><h3>Ammo, Backpack and Hotbar</h3><p>In this shoot.io, you will have limited space for your equipment. Thus, you must manage your inventory well. You can't take every item with you. There are 5 ammo slots, 5 backpack slots and 5 hotbar slots. Use each of the slots effectively. To declare victory, a well-managed inventory is a must. Get the most essential items with you.</p><h3>The Game Modes of Voxiom</h3><p>You have four game modes: Capture the Gems, Battle Royale, Survival and Free for All. There is an additional Custom Game mode that you can unlock at the 60th level. Each of these game modes serves a different purpose. But what they all have in common is that you must survive. Here, you are open to all kinds of attacks in this open world. Learn to defend yourself!</p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Capture the Gems: </strong>There are two teams in the mode: Ruby and Sapphire. The red ones are ruby soldiers, while the blue ones are sapphires. The aim is to capture the gems of the opponent team and eliminate rivals one by one. To win the game, get the highest points.</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Battle Royale:</strong> In the Battle Royale mode, you will start skydiving with a parachute after waiting in the lobby. Find a chest or a building on the map and land on it carefully. Get stuff from the chests, but only the necessary ones. And stay away from the toxic fog circle.</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Survival: </strong>You will spawn randomly on the map in the Survival mode. Your objective is to build and craft items. Take a look around and gather the resources. Try not to get killed by an enemy!</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Free for All: </strong>You can team up with players in other modes. But here, everyone is on their own. It lasts for ten minutes. The player with the highest score in this short period wins. We recommend you find the secret room and cover yourself!</li></ul><h2>Controls</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>WASD:</strong> Move</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Spacebar:</strong> Jump</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>X:</strong> Open inventory</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>C:</strong> Crouch</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>G:</strong> Drop item</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>E:</strong> Interact</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>M:</strong> Open map</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>T: </strong>Spray blocks</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Shift:</strong> Run</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Shift + Space:</strong> Jump 2 blocks high</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Tab:</strong> Pause</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Left-Click:</strong> Shoot/Use</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Right-Click/F:</strong> Aim/Switch between block placements</li></ul><h2>Developer</h2><p>Voxiom io is developed by Voxiom.</p><h2>Similar Games</h2><p>Voxiom io is a perfect blend of sandbox and shooting games. Nonetheless, we also recommend that you try <a>Miniblox io</a>. Engage in the game's parkour maps, survival maps, and other mini-maps. Let your creativity speak!</p><p>If you are looking for more options, look for other <a>Minecraft games online</a> on OnlineGames.io. There are dozens of free online game options of many kinds on the site. Please bookmark this website to access them easily!</p><figure></figure></div>",
