      "play_url": "https://craftnite.io/",
      "description": "<div><p>Ever pondered how long Minecraft Steve would last in Fortnite's battle royale chaos? Sure, he's the master of gathering tools and crafting, but when it comes to gunfights, would he be as skilled? There's only one way to find out: dive into <strong>Craftnite</strong>. This game is the ultimate crossover where Minecraft's blocky charm meets Fortnite's survival-of-the-fittest vibe.</p><p>Imagine if your two favorite TV shows decided to have a crossover episode - that's <strong>Craftnite</strong> for you. Here, you're not just surviving; you're thriving in a voxel-based world where you jump, climb, gather and engage in multiplayer battles.</p><p>So, load up this browser game and experience the thrill of being the last one standing in a world where blocks meet combat in the most fun way.</p><h2>Controls</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>WASD: </strong>Move</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Space: </strong>Jump</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Left click:</strong> Use item</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>1, 2, 3, 4: </strong>Switch item</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Enter:</strong> Toggle Chat</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Tab:</strong> Inventory</li></ul><h2>How to Play CraftNite</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\">Your journey begins with just a pickaxe. Explore this Minecraft-like world, where every block could hold the key to your next weapon.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Look for blocks shaped like weapons. Break them to snag everything from pistols to ping pong balls, sniper rifles to swords.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">You have four quick-access item slots. Switch between tools and weapons using the number keys for tactical flexibility.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">If you'd like to check your full inventory, press the tab.Â Â </li><li aria-level=\"1\">Build and climb over walls and ramps. Shooting down on your foes gives you a tactical edge. It's not just about having the high ground; it's about owning it.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Use your resources and wits to last longer than anyone else.</li></ul><h2>More Minecraft Games</h2><p>Craftnite brings the best of both worlds: Minecraft's blocky, creative freedom with Fortnite's survival and combat action. If you love strategy, crafting, and fighting, this is the game for you. If you like the style of Craftnite, you might enjoy other blocky battle games like <a>Krunker.io</a>. It also delivers fun multiplayer battles on maps like CraftNite.</p><h2>Can I play Craftnite on mobile?</h2><p>Currently, Craftnite is available as a browser game on desktops and laptops. A mobile version is not yet available, but you can play it on devices like Chromebooks.</p><h2>How do I win Craftnite?</h2><p>To win in Craftnite, you need to be the last player standing. Gather weapons and outlast the other players in the battle royale-style game. You can check the leadeboard and kill counts on the topright corner of your screen.</p><h2>Can I play Craftnite for free?</h2><p>Yes, Craftnite is completely free to play in your browser, no downloads required.</p><h2>Release Date</h2><p>October 2019</p><figure></figure></div>",
