      "description": "<div><p><strong>Time Shooter 3: SWAT</strong> is the new sequel to the first-person shooter series where time only moves when you do, inspired by the <strong>SuperHot</strong> game and designed by GoGoMan.</p><p>You'll be in charge of the time again. If you move fast, time also moves fast and vice versa. We know that Einstein proved that time is relative. But this game interprets the whole relativity theory in a new and fun way. Time Shooter 3 SWAT is a game where developers took the Matrix's bullet time and said, \"Let's make this into a game where your every twitch <strong>controls the flow of time</strong>!\"</p><p>In this new chapter of Time Shooter, you will be a SWAT(Special Weapons And Tactics) operative tasked with a dangerous mission. Terrorists have stolen SWAT gear and taken hostages. Now, it's your job to breach their hideout and eliminate the terrorists. So far, the main goal may seem familiar from the other Time Shooter games. But there's an added challenge: <strong>rescuing the hostages</strong> without a scratch. You cannot harm any hostage while battling with the terrorists, heavily armed than ever, wearing body armor and helmets and using shields to protect themselves. And, if you count on the core mechanic where time only moves when you do, beware that is both a blessing and a curse. So, you'll need to move carefully and plan your shots to avoid hitting any hostages, as even one mistake will force you to restart. Switch between pistols, machine guns, and shotguns like a PRO and bring down the enemy while dodging bullets in slow motion.</p><h2>More Games Like This</h2><p>If you enjoyed Time Shooter 3: SWAT, you might also like other Shoot'Em All style games. For example, <a>FNAF Shooter</a> might be just what you've been looking for if you want whimsical chaos. You will hunt down haunted animatronics in a shopping mall. The horror theme and chaotic gameplay will keep you hooked from the beginning.Â </p><h2>Controls</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>Move Mouse: </strong>Aim</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>WASD: </strong>Movement</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>LMB: </strong>Shoot</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>RMB: </strong>Throw</li><li aria-level=\"1\"><strong>F:</strong> Pick Up</li></ul><h2>How to Play Time Shooter 3: SWAT</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\">Start the mission by pressing Start and prepare for action.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">As a SWAT operative whose gear is stolen, you'll start without any gun.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Move around using WASD and find the desk with stolen weapons. Make your choice among them wisely; you can carry only one weapon at a time. Aim with the mouse and shoot with the left mouse button.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">When you run out of ammo, look for another weapon in the arena to keep defending yourself. You can pick up weapons dropped by enemies to stay armed.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Watch out for enemies using shields or wearing armor as they approach.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">To breach doors, use the right mouse button to throw a battering ram.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Be strategic and aim carefully â if you accidentally shoot a hostage, you'll have to restart the level.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Use the Shift key to sprint, but keep your movements calculated to avoid triggering enemy fire. While playing defensive, the slower, the better.</li></ul><h2>Dodge Bullets in Slow Motion</h2><ul><li aria-level=\"1\">Use slow motion to dodge bullets, and make your moves more precise.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">When facing armored enemies, aim for their weak spots to take them down faster.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">You have 3 shields at each level, protecting you from enemy attacks. If you consume them, all you need to do is repeat that level.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">You can grab invulnerability or endless ammo boosters in the main menu by watching a short ad.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">The major difference in this sequel of Time Shooter is the hostages. Always be mindful of hostages if you accidentally hit one of them; the game is over.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">Use your environment to your advantage. Throw objects or breach doors with the battering ram to change the flow of battle.</li><li aria-level=\"1\">As you progress, terrorists will become more aggressive and use advanced tactics. Stay alert!</li></ul><h2>Developer</h2><p>Time Shooter 3: SWAT was developed by GoGoMan, known for its creative shooters. You can also play <a>Time Shooter 1</a> and <a>Time Shooter 2</a> games on OnlineGames.io.</p><figure></figure></div>",
